{"tid":2092601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新郎患武漢肺炎，堅持舉行婚禮，傳染111賓客。","createTime":"2020-07-03T09:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T12:58:28.000Z","uid":202464,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb656e32102b0dbd3f978bb03bc2da05db6f1ba0","tid":2092601,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"印度一名26歲新郎是軟件工程師，返回巴特那市（Patna）家鄉，準備在6月中旬舉行婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n親屬說新郎在婚前幾天已有頭痛和嘔吐症狀，男方家長怕婚禮改期會造成「龐大財政損失」，堅持婚禮如期舉行，新郎沒有接受檢測便出院。<br />\n<br />\n新郎父親否認兒子婚前不適，但承認自己跟其他家人近日均驗出對武漢肺炎呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n婚禮賓客當中111人確診，多數人都無症狀；出席新郎喪禮的人也需要自我隔離，新娘則對檢測呈陰性反應。<br />\n<br />\n這場婚禮約有300人參加，新郎的喪禮則約有200人出席。"},{"pid":"b591a2ce26d483bef93f144d846be540f5c3256c","tid":2092601,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"呢件垃圾就抵撚死啦<br />\n害111個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9121859909f5127bc4da6b1f04dbe648ce5a0f1","tid":2092601,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9811cea236f1b98d8a2885de50cc1e0147b6c770","tid":2092601,"uid":11447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"邊境需要佢"},{"pid":"1f8ff25f73a1f03dbddcf077da97241599ccfb48","tid":2092601,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9811cea236f1b98d8a2885de50cc1e0147b6c770","tid":2092601,"uid":11447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"邊境需要佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:53:40.000Z","msg":"你冇睇哂？新郞死咗喎？"},{"pid":"fe8eaf5a923718dad1a3581a8ae0627b26f771e1","tid":2092601,"uid":242444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"男人=on9"},{"pid":"a8ab31fe653b11303ff04f674392f32c29499ea1","tid":2092601,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0